        Make any allocations necessary for the following measurements.
        Parameters:
        measurementInfo - - the information about the measurement(s)
        sampleTimeMillis - - the expected sample time. (interval between the stored measurements).

      • saveMeasurements

        void saveMeasurements(long tableId,
                      long timeStampMillis,
                      long... measurements)

        Save measurements.
        Parameters:
        tableId - - the table ID to store measurements for.
        timeStampMillis - - the timestamp of the measurement (milliseconds since Jan 1 1970 UTC)

      • query

        @Nullable
MeasurementStoreQuery query()
        Returns:
        a query-able interface for the store. Not all stores will be directly query-able, like most remote stores. This method will apply usually only to node local stores.
